HEADWORD: Permanganic
<hw>Per`man*gan"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Pertaining to, or designating, one of the higher acids of
manganese, <chform>HMnO4</chform>, which forms salts called
<xex>permanganates</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
